review_blob: This one is unbelievable. Great nose beautiful color. Excellent flavor and a just a damn good overall beer
Very fruity. Great nose. Bold flavor. Coffee and chocolate Flavors to the front of the line. 9.5 aBV makes it even better.
This secondary fermented ales have neither been pasteurized nor filtered and only natural ingredients are used. Great combination of fresh hops and yeast of the chimay cinq cents.
This Belgian golden ale is one of my personal favorites. From the aroma,the color to the taste it is a winner all around.
